metadata.label: join_accounts_and_opportunities
metadata.comment: Joins account and opportunity data based on the account ID, retrieving relevant fields from both datasets.

metadata.label: Select_Fields
metadata.comment: Selects specific fields from the input data, including account ID, amount, expected revenue, and the quarter in which the account was closed.

expression.expression: concat(CAST(year(to_date(CloseDate)) AS STRING), 'Q', CAST(quarter(CloseDate) AS STRING))

metadata.label: aggregate_by_account
metadata.comment: Aggregates data by account, providing information on the number of opportunities, total amount, expected revenue, and the most recent closed quarter.
